snippet.textDisplay: I got my booster 3 months ago and I tested positive on Saturday. No symptoms until Monday where I had a bad cough which was persistent. This carried onto the next day, and this morning. I woke up at 3 and my chest hurt really bad, and it was impossible for me to sleep. I had a really bad cough and runny nose. School starts in a few days, and I hope this doesn’t continue.
